column5: All the very best to you my friend and I hope MB gives you everything you want today!
Happy B-Day Norm, all the best to ya !!
Happy Birthday Beans!  Too bad you can't go out and chase some carp on your b-day, but soon enough.  Cheers!
Happy birthday Norm.  Have a great day cat.
Have a great day Norm!  S.
Happy Birthday Beans.  Reckon you've been at legal drinking age for quite a while by now.
Enjoy the Day Beansie. Have a good one.
Happy Birthday Norm best of the day to you my friend.   Art
Happy Birthday Norm!!!
Hey Have a great birthday
HAPPY BIRTHDAY my friend hope you have a fantastic day  will be up soon for crappies my treat
Older than a rock, smarter than a fox, about as handsom as a coon coming out of hybernation but one heck of a good man!

Older than a rock, smarter than a fox, about as handsom as a coon coming out of hybernation but one heck of a good man! Come on Cliff we all know that is not true  Older than a Rock Yes Heck of a good man yes the other 2 ask MB about that

Thanks for all the swell wishes my friends...MB took me out for Chinese then we stopped at Timmies and picked up half a dozen Bavarian cream filled donuts...And I wondered why my glucose reading was so "high" this morning...LOL
MB took me out for Chinese  Cody Inn at Buckhorn Norm ??
Cody Inn at Buckhorn Norm ?? That was my first choice Lew but they are closed on Tuesday...  Wok-on-the-Lake in Bobcaygeon...nothing special but decent food...  http://www.wokonthelake.com/
OK Norm, I know that place, we ate there a few months back after buying some shoes at Bigley's.  We also like Cody's and were there for supper last Friday evening.

x3 Norm!!,sounds like you had a good one!!
